library(tidyverse)

data.frame(
    x = rnorm(20),
    y = rnorm(20),
    shape = rep(c("smiley", "poop"), 10)
) |> 
    ggplot(aes(x, y, shape = shape)) +
    geom_point(size = 10) +
    scale_shape_manual(
        labels = c(smiley = "Completed Study", poop = "Pooped"),
        values = c(smiley = "😀", poop = "💩"),
        guide = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 5))
    ) +
    theme_classic()
